intradyn.selenium.addons
Class SelHelpers

java.lang.Object
  intradyn.selenium.addons.SelHelpers

public class SelHelpers
extends Object

Class SelHelpers The SelHelpers class are a collection of methods I have written or found which are useful extensions of functionality from Selenium 2.0 * The shortDelay method is written as such just to reduce the amount of typing in the test cases. verifyTextPresent is a method which searches the entire page displayed and returns true if ANY part of the page contains ALL of the text specified. Note this means the entire query must occur in a single element / div on the page. isElementPresent determines whether or not a specific WebElement (div, h, etc.) exists on the page.
